  "body": "Sometimes when the full importer is running as well as the in-sync importer is running there can be a lot of thread contention around MainnetBlockImporter.importBlock.  We should investigate if that method needs to be synchronized and if it can be removed or the synchronized blocks made finer grained.\r\n\r\n",
