    "body": "Java flight Recorder and JDK Mission Control\r\n\r\nOn the box being monitored:\r\n\r\n```\r\nsudo jcmd\r\n# ... one of the processes listed will be besu, note the pid, which is 1234 for this sample\r\nsudo jcmd 1234 JFR.start duration=60s filename=/tmp/besurecording.jfr\r\n```\r\n\r\nI then scp the .jfr file, open it in JDK Mission Control, go to the Lock Instances page, select a specific thread, and the stack traces on the bottom can be copied.",
